{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/XcodePreviewSupport"},"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Architecture-and-Best-Practices","title":"Architecture and Best Practices","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/ModularArchitecture","doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/SOLIDPrinciples"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Dependencies that hit the network, access the file system, or perform heavy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"computation are problematic in Xcode Previews. Forge lets you provide a ","type":"text"},{"code":"preview","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"factory that is used automatically when running inside a preview — no conditional","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"checks needed in your view code.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"text":"The preview Parameter","type":"heading","anchor":"The-preview-Parameter"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pass a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"preview"},{"type":"text","text":" closure to "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/Container\/provide(_:key:_:preview:)"},{"type":"text","text":" alongside the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"normal factory:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["public var authService: any AuthServiceProtocol {","    provide(.singleton) {","        AuthService(network: self.networkClient)","    } preview: {","        MockAuthService()","    }","}","","public var networkClient: any NetworkClientProtocol {","    provide(.singleton) {","        URLSessionNetworkClient()","    } preview: {","        MockNetworkClient()","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the code runs inside an Xcode Preview, "},{"code":"MockAuthService()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is returned. In"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"production, "},{"code":"AuthService(network:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is returned."}]},{"level":2,"text":"How Preview Detection Works","type":"heading","anchor":"How-Preview-Detection-Works"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Forge detects the preview environment by checking for the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"XCODE_RUNNING_FOR_PREVIEWS"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"environment variable, which Xcode sets to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"1\""},{"type":"text","text":" when rendering previews. This is the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"standard detection mechanism used across the Swift community."}]},{"level":3,"text":"Resolution Precedence","type":"heading","anchor":"Resolution-Precedence"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/Container\/provide(_:key:_:preview:)","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is called, resolution follows this order:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Overrides"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — always checked first (test overrides take priority)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Preview factory"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — used if running in a preview and a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"preview"},{"type":"text","text":" closure was provided"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Normal factory","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — the default production path","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Preview-Values-Are-Never-Cached","type":"heading","text":"Preview Values Are Never Cached"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Preview factories are called fresh on every resolution, regardless of the declared","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/Scope","type":"reference"},{"text":". Even if a dependency is registered as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".singleton"},{"text":", the preview factory","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"runs every time in a preview context. This ensures previews always reflect the latest","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"mock state.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"When-to-Provide-a-Preview-Factory","type":"heading","text":"When to Provide a Preview Factory"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Provide one for:","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Network clients and API services","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Database and file system access"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Analytics and logging services"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Any dependency that performs I\/O or has side effects"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Skip it for:"}]}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pure in-memory services (formatters, validators, parsers)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Simple value types or data transformations"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Dependencies that already work correctly without network access","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Multiple-Preview-Variants","type":"heading","text":"Multiple Preview Variants"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use different overrides within "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"type":"text","text":" blocks to show different states:"}]},{"code":["#Preview(\"Logged In\") {","    AuthContainer.shared.override(\\.authService) {","        MockAuthService(isLoggedIn: true)","    }","    return ProfileView()","}","","#Preview(\"Logged Out\") {","    AuthContainer.shared.override(\\.authService) {","        MockAuthService(isLoggedIn: false)","    }","    return ProfileView()","}","","#Preview(\"Error State\") {","    AuthContainer.shared.override(\\.authService) {","        MockAuthService(shouldFail: true)","    }","    return ProfileView()","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This lets you preview the same view in multiple states without changing any production"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"code."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Testing Preview Behavior","type":"heading","anchor":"Testing-Preview-Behavior","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The framework includes an internal ","type":"text"},{"code":"_isPreviewOverride","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property (accessible via","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"@testable import","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") that lets tests simulate the preview environment:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["@testable import Forge","","PreviewContext._isPreviewOverride = true","defer { PreviewContext._isPreviewOverride = nil }","","\/\/ Dependencies now use their preview factories","let service = MyContainer.shared.authService","\/\/ service is MockAuthService"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tests using "},{"type":"codeV